structures.vectors

Interface Vector<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic Type
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataStructure<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    List<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayList, LinkedList, Queue, Stack

    public interface Vector<T>
extends DataStructure<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Interface for all linear DataStructures such as LinkedList, ArrayList, or any other vector-like data structure.
